<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Interview Scheduled</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); }
        h1 { color: #1a73e8; text-align: center; }
        p { color: #666666; line-height: 1.6; }
        .details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .qr-code { text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 0.9em; color: #999999; margin-top: 20px; }
        .highlight { color: #1a73e8; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Interview Scheduled</h1>
        <p>Dear {{ application.firstName }},</p>
        <p>We are pleased to inform you that your interview has been scheduled. Below are the details:</p>
        <div class="details">
            <p><span class="highlight">Date:</span> {{ interview.interviewDate|date('Y-m-d H:i') }}</p>
            <p><span class="highlight">Location:</span> {{ interview.location }}</p>
            <p><span class="highlight">Interview ID:</span> {{ interview.id }}</p>
            <p><span class="highlight">Meeting Link:</span>
                <a href="{{ meetingLink }}">{{ meetingLink }}</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <p>Please scan the QR code below to access your interview details quickly:</p>
        <p>We look forward to speaking with you. If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>WorkFlow</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
